messages.message:
Workspaces are now GA and live on AI Hub prod! I encourage internal users to create team-based workspaces and for our growth team to help set up workspaces for our commercial customers (cc: @Tom @Lee).

You can move projects across workspaces by clicking the three dots on the project card in My Hub. This is useful if you have a project built in a personal workspace and you'd like to share it with your team.

As always, please try out and share feedback in this channel to help us keep improving!
More details in the original post here: https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C0516UPPMT3/p1701134192520119
